The paper deals with stochastic video prediction models, which are commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The model introduced in the paper also involves generating a latent representation, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also applies the framework to a 3D scene reconstruction dataset, which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
